Selective use of insecticides may be 
considered when sanitation measures 
fail to control fly problems. Fly baits 
used for control of house flies are not 
likely to provide good control of blow 
flies because the attractants present in 
fly baits were designed to attract house 
flies rather than blow flies. However, 
when placed on the ground surround -
