# Director's Rules v4.0 Gap Analysis

**Canonical target:** `2026-07-07-directors-rules-v4.0.docx`  
**Legacy reference:** `2026-07-07-directors-rules-legacy-copy.pdf` (09/2007; SOG edit 12/2019)  
**Do not publish:** `2026-07-07-directors-rules-ai-export-DRAFT-NOT-FOR-PUBLICATION.md`

## Status

v4.0 improves structure (At a Glance, Must/Should/May, multilingual block, Appendix B disease table) but **jumps from Section III to Section VIII** in the body. Sections IV–VII are referenced in the TOC and At a Glance but are not fully drafted.

## Rules to use until v4.0 Sections IV–VI are restored

| Rule | Legacy PDF | v4.0.docx | HHVC publishable copy |
|------|------------|-----------|------------------------|
| Owner investigates pest reports | **§V.2 within 72 hours** | "Respond promptly" (no hours) | **72 hours** — cite legacy §V.2 |
| PCO adjacent units | **§VI.6 all adjacent units inspected/treated** | Missing §VI body | **All adjacent units** — cite legacy §VI.6 |
| Landscape clearance | **§VII.3 at least 3 feet** | "away from buildings" (no number) | **3 feet** enforcement; **6 feet** PPBD design best practice |
| Fence clear space | **24 inches** | vague | **24 inches** — cite legacy §VII |
| Gap sealing | **¼ inch** (v4.0 Section VIII aligns) | Section VIII | **¼ inch** |
| General HHVC phone | 3805 in legacy tenant line | **415-252-3800** / 311 | **3800** / 311 |
| Mosquito/WNV | 3806 in legacy | unified to 3800 | **3800** unless program confirms separate line |

## Three distinct timelines (do not conflate)

1. **Tenant 72-hour written notice** before 311 — program-manager rule + Compliance xlsx (not Article 11A alone).
2. **Owner 72-hour investigation** — Director's Rules §V.2 (legacy PDF until v4.0 §V restored).
3. **Bed bug PCO response** — Article 11A / bed bug Director's Rules: **two working days** (not 72 hours).

## Adjacent-unit inspection

Legacy §VI.6: *"All units adjacent to the infested unit shall be inspected and treated if necessary."*

This is a **general PCO duty**, not bed-bug-only. Bed bugs add the separate two-working-day timeline and K9/adjoining-room operational detail (Pestec).
</file>

