# Pestec IPM Guidelines for Multifamily Housing (extract)

Source: `2026-07-07-pestec-ipm-multifamily-housing.pdf` (SF Environment / Pestec, CDC REACH)

Supplementary operations guidance for SFHA-style multi-unit housing. Not Health Code.

## Six IPM pillars

1. Inspection, monitoring, recordkeeping
2. Pest exclusion and structural repair
3. Sanitation
4. Reduced-risk pesticides (last resort)
5. Communication
6. Education

## Measurable standards (Appendix F toolkit)

- Cockroach gaps: 1/8 inch
- Mouse gaps: 1/4 inch
- Seal with steel wool or copper mesh before caulk; door sweeps; vent screens
- Prohibit OTC sprays, foggers, bug bombs, unlabeled pesticides

